* Azure Data\nFactory (ADF)
** Role
***_ Orchestration layer
***_ Data movement platform
** Best For
***_ Microsoft services (Dynamics 365, Azure SQL)
***_ Landing data into ADLS for Databricks
***_ Multi-service workflow coordination
** Not Best For
***_ Native Databricks transformations
***_ Real-time data processing
** Integration Pattern
***_ ADF lands data in cloud storage
***_ Databricks processes from storage
@endmindmap
